(B) Direct each school managed and controlled by the local board of education
to publish the board's policy on the use of artificial intelligence by students, teachers,
and staff for instructional and assignment purposes on the school's website.
SECTION 3. This act takes effect July 1, 2026, the public welfare requiring it.
